{"about_the_game":"Peg Solitaire is a game that is relaxing, and challenging all at the same time.<br><br>The rules are simple, you take one peg, and you jump over another peg in any direction as long as there is an empty hole to jump to.<br><br>The goal is to leave only a single peg left, sounds simple, but can be pretty complex.<br><br>Earn points by jumping pegs, and a big bonus more by winning the game.<br><br>Use earned points to unlock new boards and pegs!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>Features</u></strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 Starter game boards, and 8 unlockable game boards.<br></li><li> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629160/extras/Unlockable_Boards_Small.png?t=1622216202\" /><br></li><li> 2 Starter pegs, and 8 unlockable pegs.<br></li><li> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629160/extras/Unlockable_Pegs_Small.png?t=1622216202\" /><br></li><li> A randomized starter hole for repeatability of boards without constantly playing the same thing.<br></li><li> An option to randomize the peg and board used when playing continuously so as to not play the same board or use the same peg every round.<br></li><li> Encouraging words to keep you going through your losses.</li></ul><br>To use controllers or the keyboard for playing the game you must tick the gamepad checkbox in the settings menu.<br><br>Having an issue? Want to report a bug directly or need help?<br><br>Join my discord and shoot me a message! ","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1622216202","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629160/page.bg.jpg?t=1622216202","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1622216202","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st